originContent: # Reactive Resume
translatedContent: # Reactive Resume

originContent: A free and open-source resume builder that simplifies the process of creating, updating, and sharing your resume.
translatedContent: A free and open-source resume builder that simplifies the process of creating, updating, and sharing your resume.

originContent: ### [Go to App](https://rxresu.me/) | [Docs](https://docs.rxresu.me/)
translatedContent: ### [Go to App](https://rxresu.me/) | [Docs](https://docs.rxresu.me/)

originContent: ## Description
translatedContent: ## Description

originContent: Reactive Resume is a free and open-source resume builder that simplifies the process of creating, updating, and sharing your resume. With zero user tracking or advertising, your privacy is a top priority. The platform is extremely user-friendly and can be self-hosted in less than 30 seconds if you wish to own your data completely.
translatedContent: Reactive Resume is a free and open-source resume builder that simplifies the process of creating, updating, and sharing your resume. With zero user tracking or advertising, your privacy is a top priority. The platform is extremely user-friendly and can be self-hosted in less than 30 seconds if you wish to own your data completely.

originContent: It's available in multiple languages and comes packed with features such as real-time editing, dozens of templates, drag-and-drop customisation, and integration with OpenAI for enhancing your writing.
translatedContent: It's available in multiple languages and comes packed with features such as real-time editing, dozens of templates, drag-and-drop customisation, and integration with OpenAI for enhancing your writing.

originContent: You can share a personalised link of your resume to potential employers, track its views or downloads, and customise your page layout by dragging-and-dropping sections. The platform also supports various font options and provides dozens of templates to choose from. And yes, there's even a dark mode for a more comfortable viewing experience.
translatedContent: You can share a personalised link of your resume to potential employers, track its views or downloads, and customise your page layout by dragging-and-dropping sections. The platform also supports various font options and provides dozens of templates to choose from. And yes, there's even a dark mode for a more comfortable viewing experience.

originContent: Start creating your standout resume with Reactive Resume today!
translatedContent: Start creating your standout resume with Reactive Resume today!

originContent: ## Features
translatedContent: ## Features

originContent: - **Free, forever** and open-source
translatedContent: - **Free, forever** and open-source

originContent: - No telemetry, user tracking or advertising
translatedContent: - No telemetry, user tracking or advertising

originContent: - You can self-host the application in less than 30 seconds
translatedContent: - You can self-host the application in less than 30 seconds

originContent: - **Available in multiple languages** ([help add/improve your language here](https://translate.rxresu.me/))
translatedContent: - **Available in multiple languages** ([help add/improve your language here](https://translate.rxresu.me/))

originContent: - Use your email address (or a throw-away address, no problem) to create an account
translatedContent: - Use your email address (or a throw-away address, no problem) to create an account

originContent: - You can also sign in with your GitHub or Google account, and even set up two-factor authentication for extra security
translatedContent: - You can also sign in with your GitHub or Google account, and even set up two-factor authentication for extra security

originContent: - Create as many resumes as you like under a single account, optimising each resume for every job application based on its description for a higher ATS score
translatedContent: - Create as many resumes as you like under a single account, optimising each resume for every job application based on its description for a higher ATS score

originContent: - **Bring your own OpenAI API key** and unlock features such as improving your writing, fixing spelling and grammar or changing the tone of your text in one-click
translatedContent: - **Bring your own OpenAI API key** and unlock features such as improving your writing, fixing spelling and grammar or changing the tone of your text in one-click

originContent: - Translate your resume into any language using ChatGPT and import it back for easier editing
translatedContent: - Translate your resume into any language using ChatGPT and import it back for easier editing

originContent: - Create single page resumes or a resume that spans multiple pages easily
translatedContent: - Create single page resumes or a resume that spans multiple pages easily

originContent: - Customize the colours and layouts to add a personal touch to your resume
translatedContent: - Customize the colours and layouts to add a personal touch to your resume

originContent: - Customise your page layout as you like just by dragging-and-dropping sections
translatedContent: - Customise your page layout as you like just by dragging-and-dropping sections

originContent: - Create custom sections that are specific to your industry if the existing ones don't fit
translatedContent: - Create custom sections that are specific to your industry if the existing ones don't fit

originContent: - Jot down personal notes specific to your resume that's only visible to you
translatedContent: - Jot down personal notes specific to your resume that's only visible to you

originContent: - Lock a resume to prevent making any further edits (useful for master templates)
translatedContent: - Lock a resume to prevent making any further edits (useful for master templates)

originContent: - **Dozens of templates** to choose from, ranging from professional to modern
translatedContent: - **Dozens of templates** to choose from, ranging from professional to modern

originContent: - Design your resume using the standardised EuroPass design template
translatedContent: - Design your resume using the standardised EuroPass design template

originContent: - Supports printing resumes in A4 or Letter page formats
translatedContent: - Supports printing resumes in A4 or Letter page formats

originContent: - Design your resume with any font that's available on [Google Fonts](https://fonts.google.com/)
translatedContent: - Design your resume with any font that's available on [Google Fonts](https://fonts.google.com/)

originContent: - **Share a personalised link of your resume** to companies or recruiters for them to get the latest updates
translatedContent: - **Share a personalised link of your resume** to companies or recruiters for them to get the latest updates

originContent: - You can track the number of views or downloads your public resume has received
translatedContent: - You can track the number of views or downloads your public resume has received

originContent: - Built with state-of-the-art (at the moment) and dependable technologies that's battle tested and peer reviewed by the open-source community on GitHub
translatedContent: - Built with state-of-the-art (at the moment) and dependable technologies that's battle tested and peer reviewed by the open-source community on GitHub

originContent: - **MIT License**, so do what you like with the code as long as you credit the original author
translatedContent: - **MIT License**, so do what you like with the code as long as you credit the original author

originContent: - And yes, there’s a dark mode too 🌓
translatedContent: - And yes, there’s a dark mode too 🌓

originContent: ## Built With
translatedContent: ## Built With

originContent: - React (Vite), for the frontend
translatedContent: - React (Vite), for the frontend

originContent: - NestJS, for the backend
translatedContent: - NestJS, for the backend

originContent: - Postgres (primary database)
translatedContent: - Postgres (primary database)

originContent: - Prisma ORM, which frees you to switch to any other relational database with a few minor changes in the code
translatedContent: - Prisma ORM, which frees you to switch to any other relational database with a few minor changes in the code

originContent: - Minio (for object storage: to store avatars, resume PDFs and previews)
translatedContent: - Minio (for object storage: to store avatars, resume PDFs and previews)

originContent: - Browserless (for headless chrome, to print PDFs and generate previews)
translatedContent: - Browserless (for headless chrome, to print PDFs and generate previews)

originContent: - SMTP Server (to send password recovery emails)
translatedContent: - SMTP Server (to send password recovery emails)

originContent: - GitHub/Google OAuth (for quickly authenticating users)
translatedContent: - GitHub/Google OAuth (for quickly authenticating users)

originContent: - LinguiJS and Crowdin (for translation management and localization)
translatedContent: - LinguiJS and Crowdin (for translation management and localization)
